86
00:06:24,060 --> 00:06:24,860
Think about it.

87
00:06:24,860 --> 00:06:26,820
Would a purposeful fake son

88
00:06:26,980 --> 00:06:28,300
be so impatient

89
00:06:28,380 --> 00:06:29,900
