90
00:06:30,340 --> 00:06:31,700
under the nose of his father?

91
00:06:32,300 --> 00:06:33,420
As long as you do something

92
00:06:33,540 --> 00:06:34,980
a fake son would never do,

93
00:06:35,500 --> 00:06:36,820
