pass off the fake as the real thing.

94
00:06:37,660 --> 00:06:38,580
No.

95
00:06:38,740 --> 00:06:39,980
I can't drag you into the water.

96
00:06:40,260 --> 00:06:41,100
Do you remember when we

97
00:06:41,180 --> 00:06:42,500
